#arthurnery #isalang #vivarecords
The Official Music Video of 'Isa Lang' by Arthur Nery starring Arthur Nery & Kaila Estrada

Let Arthur Nery’s 'Isa Lang' take you through a spectrum of feelings — a neo-soul journey filled with heartfelt verses and soulful hooks.Isa Lang is a beautiful journey through the highs and lows of emotional truth, showcasing Arthur Nery’s unique ability to blend soulful melodies with heartfelt storytelling. Prepare to be moved, mesmerized, and taken on a profound emotional ride like no other.

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
First hunt. Last chance.

From the director of Prey, watch the brand-new trailer for Predator: Badlands, in theaters November 7.

“Predator: Badlands,” which stars Elle Fanning and Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, is set in the future on a remote planet, where a young Predator, outcast from his clan, finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Fanning) and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. The film is directed by Dan Trachtenberg and produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt, Brent O’Connor.

The fall of 1987. Hawkins is scarred by the opening of the Rifts, and our heroes are united by a single goal: find and kill Vecna. But he has vanished — his whereabouts and plans unknown. Complicating their mission, the government has placed the town under military quarantine and intensified its hunt for Eleven, forcing her back into hiding. As the anniversary of Will’s disappearance approaches, so does a heavy, familiar dread. The final battle is looming — and with it, a darkness more powerful and more deadly than anything they’ve faced before. 👹  Apocalypto 2 Concept

Nearly two decades after the release of Mel Gibson’s groundbreaking 2006 film Apocalypto, fan speculation has reignited online about a possible sequel — a spiritual continuation that could explore the collapse of the Aztec Empire as Spanish conquistadors arrive.

While there has been no official confirmation from Gibson or any studio, film forums and fan pages have been abuzz with the idea that Apocalypto 2 could be in development — or at least being quietly workshopped. The original film ended with the dramatic arrival of Spanish ships off the Mesoamerican coast, hinting at the massive historical change to come. According to fan theories, the sequel could pick up from that moment, focusing on the cultural clash, resistance, and tragic fall of indigenous empires in the face of European conquest.

Some online rumors even suggest that Gibson has been quietly researching pre-Columbian history beyond the Mayan civilization and might shift focus to the Aztec capital of Tenochtitlán, where a new set of characters would face both internal political strife and the external threat of Hernán Cortés’ advancing forces.

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle  |  OFFICIAL THEME SONG TRAILER (LiSA)
snippet.description:
The final battle ignites as Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle premieres September 12 only in theatres! 🔥

[ THEME SONGS ] 
🎵 “Shine in the Cruel Night” by LiSA

LISTEN NOW: https://lisa.lnk.to/ShineintheCruelNight

Official Website: https://demonslayer-anime.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/demonslayer.anime/
X: https://x.com/demonslayerusa

About Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle:
Tanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon. 

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.
The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. 

And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

snippet.description:
SLOW ROCK MEDLEY COLLECTION 2025 💖 BEST LUMANG TUGTUGIN 90S 💖 NONSTOP SLOW ROCK LOVE SONGS

🎸 Slow Rock Medley Collection 2025

Step back in time and feel the emotion of the 90s slow rock era with this heartfelt nonstop medley of Lumang Tugtugin (Old Songs). Featuring the most memorable Pinoy love songs and soft rock ballads, this collection is perfect for those who cherish timeless melodies and soul-stirring lyrics.

💿 What to Expect:

Nonstop slow rock hits from the 80s & 90s

Classic OPM love songs that never fade

Signature selections from the Emerson Condino Collection

Seamless transitions, no talking, no ads – just pure music

💘 Ideal for:

Relaxing alone or with loved ones

Reminiscing old memories

Long road trips and peaceful nights

Fans of sentimental Filipino music

🎧 Let the music bring you back to a simpler time when lyrics were deep, voices were raw, and every song told a story.

📌 Don’t forget to LIKE, SHARE, and SUBSCRIBE for more nonstop medleys and nostalgic OPM playlists!
